            </rs>, aged 27.</p>
               <p>Palmer, <rs id="t18031026-56-verdict329" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18031026-56-verdict329" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18031026-56-verdict329" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>, aged 24.</p>
               <p>Of stealing, but not of the burglary.</p>
